    note right of UnboundUnconnected
        Created with DatagramSocket(DatagramSocketImpl impl) or DatagramSocket(null).
        bind() must be called before send/receive.
        bind() throws if already bound.
    end note

    note right of BoundConnected
        connect() restricts send/receive to the connected address.
        disconnect() returns to BoundUnconnected.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. close() is idempotent.
        setOption/getOption throw IOException if closed.
        setReuseAddress throws SocketException if closed.
    end note
